Usage: label_tower [--help] [--version] [--directory VAR] labels

Find files and directories with the required labels.

Positional arguments:
  labels           the list of labels to search for. [nargs: 0 or more] 

Optional arguments:
  -h, --help       shows help message and exits 
  -v, --version    prints version information and exits 
  -d, --directory  specify the directory to start from. [nargs=0..1] [default: "/work/tests"]
